{"lang":"ko","stage":7,"title":"fuller sentences","sentences":[{"t":"그 사람 3월부터 일자리 찾고 있어요.","en":"He's been looking for a job since March.","r":"geu saram samwolbuteo iljari chatgo isseoyo.","a":"n_1d8703fa3668.mp3"},{"t":"다 해서 삼십 유로예요.","en":"It all comes to thirty euros.","r":"da haeseo samsip yuroyeyo.","a":"n_1d4bae5e883c.mp3"},{"t":"우리는 한 시에 먹어요.","en":"We eat at one.","r":"urineun han sie meogeoyo.","a":"n_eeb40a8b9af1.mp3"},{"t":"저는 다섯 시에 끝나요.","en":"I finish at five.","r":"jeoneun daseot sie kkeunnayo.","a":"n_b9ba06669a99.mp3"},{"t":"일요일엔 많이 자요.","en":"On Sundays I sleep a lot.","r":"iryoiren mani jayo.","a":"n_e23eb59249dd.mp3"},{"t":"토요일엔 일 안 해요.","en":"I don't work on Saturday.","r":"toyoiren il an haeyo.","a":"n_b340f673a89c.mp3"},{"t":"목요일에 봐요.","en":"See you on Thursday.","r":"mogyoie bwayo.","a":"n_6293de33701c.mp3"},{"t":"몇 시에 시작해요?","en":"What time do we start?","r":"myeot sie sijakaeyo?","a":"n_6d5ad3fc2f0e.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 제 생일이에요.","en":"Today is my birthday.","r":"oneul je saengiri-eyo.","a":"n_55f6173c1bb3.mp3"},{"t":"또 늦었네요.","en":"You're late again.","r":"tto neujeonneyo.","a":"n_b87e70aa970b.mp3"},{"t":"둘 다 해서 얼마예요?","en":"How much are the two of them?","r":"dul da haeseo eolmayeyo?","a":"n_bf046bc1237e.mp3"},{"t":"얼마에 팔아요?","en":"How much are you selling it for?","r":"eolmae parayo?","a":"n_9b2c6b8e6bb8.mp3"},{"t":"오늘은 입장 무료예요.","en":"Getting in is free today.","r":"oneureun ipjang muryoyeyo.","a":"n_bd12c762ea61.mp3"},{"t":"배가 아파요.","en":"My stomach hurts.","r":"baega apayo.","a":"n_7bac2d6c9224.mp3"},{"t":"허리가 아파요.","en":"My back hurts.","r":"heoriga apayo.","a":"n_d4e072d659a0.mp3"},{"t":"눈이 아파요.","en":"My eyes hurt.","r":"nuni apayo.","a":"n_fb71e27e70ac.mp3"},{"t":"아나 소개할게요.","en":"Let me introduce you to Ana.","r":"ana sogaehalgeyo.","a":"n_cf472ec90025.mp3"},{"t":"집에서 심심해요.","en":"I'm bored at home.","r":"jibeseo simsimhaeyo.","a":"n_8fc47362cb8c.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 돈이 더 필요해요.","en":"She needs more money.","r":"geu saram doni deo piryohaeyo.","a":"n_f95b75d659a8.mp3"},{"t":"나중에 봐도 돼요.","en":"I can see it later.","r":"najunge bwado dwaeyo.","a":"n_8c6d69f39be2.mp3"},{"t":"올 거예요, 있을 거예요?","en":"Are you coming or staying?","r":"ol geoyeyo, isseul geoyeyo?","a":"n_a4cad6b1740d.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 저녁 만들고 있어요.","en":"She's making dinner.","r":"geu saram jeonyeok mandeulgo isseoyo.","a":"n_188a6c6e6f21.mp3"},{"t":"간단히 하나만 물어볼게요.","en":"I'll ask a quick question.","r":"gandanhi hanaman mureobolgeyo.","a":"n_1d6d90e05285.mp3"},{"t":"어젯밤에 가방 쌌어요.","en":"I packed my bag last night.","r":"eojetbame gabang ssasseoyo.","a":"n_547c963d25f7.mp3"},{"t":"웃기지 마요.","en":"Don't make me laugh.","r":"utgiji mayo.","a":"n_ecadc10b3d2d.mp3"},{"t":"나중에 얘기해 줄게요.","en":"I'll tell you about it later.","r":"najunge yaegihae julgeyo.","a":"n_8b35666e3c43.mp3"},{"t":"누가 말해 줬어요?","en":"Who told you?","r":"nuga malhae jwosseoyo?","a":"n_ca42e1fed2e8.mp3"},{"t":"저한테 아무 말도 안 해 줘요.","en":"You never tell me anything.","r":"jeohante amu maldo an hae jwoyo.","a":"n_ac47a73d3161.mp3"},{"t":"그 식당 몰라요.","en":"I don't know that restaurant.","r":"geu sikdang mollayo.","a":"n_6c1cdb0ec7ad.mp3"},{"t":"차이를 모르겠어요.","en":"I don't see the difference.","r":"chaireul moreugesseoyo.","a":"n_4df9a382a442.mp3"},{"t":"뭐 좀 보여 주고 싶어요.","en":"I want to show you something.","r":"mwo jom boyeo jugo sipeoyo.","a":"n_2e53211c3aa0.mp3"},{"t":"그렇게 쳐다보지 마요.","en":"Don't look at me like that.","r":"geureoke chyeodaboji mayo.","a":"n_d178494fc502.mp3"},{"t":"이번 주에 일 많이 해요.","en":"We're working a lot this week.","r":"ibeon jue il mani haeyo.","a":"n_addba8960522.mp3"},{"t":"빵 좀 건네줄래요?","en":"Can you pass me the bread?","r":"ppang jom geonnejullaeyo?","a":"n_1c25fc15b24a.mp3"},{"t":"제 친구들 근처에 살아요.","en":"My friends live nearby.","r":"je chingudeul geuncheoe sarayo.","a":"n_69f0d4b61bfe.mp3"},{"t":"네 시에 시작해요.","en":"We start at four.","r":"ne sie sijakaeyo.","a":"n_13076caae7d6.mp3"},{"t":"12월엔 추워요.","en":"It's cold in December.","r":"sibiworen chuwoyo.","a":"n_63f59f13ea92.mp3"},{"t":"제 시계가 틀려요.","en":"My watch is wrong.","r":"je sigyega teullyeoyo.","a":"n_cf9ffc0e29d3.mp3"},{"t":"나중에 설명할게요.","en":"I'll explain later.","r":"najunge seolmyeonghalgeyo.","a":"n_5c13afc8b90f.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 늦게 일어났어요.","en":"I got up late today.","r":"oneul neutge ireonasseoyo.","a":"n_81256de56824.mp3"},{"t":"딱 맞게 왔어요.","en":"You're right on time.","r":"ttak matge wasseoyo.","a":"n_1e81bf5a7d4b.mp3"},{"t":"카드로 내도 돼요?","en":"Can I pay by card?","r":"kadeuro naedo dwaeyo?","a":"n_fb935b566608.mp3"},{"t":"택시 어디서 세워요?","en":"Where do I stop the taxi?","r":"taeksi eodiseo sewoyo?","a":"n_01476ef7d162.mp3"},{"t":"항상 기차를 놓쳐요.","en":"I always miss the train.","r":"hangsang gichareul nochyeoyo.","a":"n_9ffb6a11782a.mp3"},{"t":"이가 하나 아파요.","en":"One of my teeth hurts.","r":"iga hana apayo.","a":"n_2cbac48abe10.mp3"},{"t":"어제 영화 보러 갔어요.","en":"Yesterday I went to the movies.","r":"eoje yeonghwa boreo gasseoyo.","a":"n_aae08cdc4ed8.mp3"},{"t":"발이 아파요.","en":"My feet hurt.","r":"bari apayo.","a":"n_5c76ed5ac79d.mp3"},{"t":"거울로 자기 모습 봐요.","en":"Look at yourself in the mirror.","r":"geoullo jagi moseup bwayo.","a":"n_7f13fa080e2f.mp3"},{"t":"한 번도 안 해 봤어요.","en":"I've never tried it.","r":"han beondo an hae bwasseoyo.","a":"n_0c453d904266.mp3"},{"t":"토요일에 어디 갔어요?","en":"Where did you go on Saturday?","r":"toyoie eodi gasseoyo?","a":"n_018c87bc93a1.mp3"},{"t":"뭐 좀 먹어야 해요.","en":"You have to eat something.","r":"mwo jom meogeoya haeyo.","a":"n_a1b586a86540.mp3"},{"t":"아니요, 그건 제가 아니에요.","en":"No, that's not me.","r":"aniyo, geugeon jega aniyeyo.","a":"n_ae7435a5e5cb.mp3"},{"t":"저는 괜찮아요, 그쪽은요?","en":"I'm good, and you?","r":"jeoneun gwaenchanayo, geujjogeunnyo?","a":"n_ee1d569419bf.mp3"},{"t":"저는 하고 싶은 대로 해요.","en":"I do what I want.","r":"jeoneun hago sipeun daero haeyo.","a":"n_19f136dd7c7f.mp3"},{"t":"저는 할 수 있는 만큼 해요.","en":"I do what I can.","r":"jeoneun hal su inneun mankeum haeyo.","a":"n_16275d4bca99.mp3"},{"t":"잠을 더 자야 해요.","en":"You have to sleep more.","r":"jameul deo jaya haeyo.","a":"n_d8cdec131be0.mp3"},{"t":"내일 일해야 해요?","en":"Do you have to work tomorrow?","r":"naeil ilhaeya haeyo?","a":"n_01bee2efa282.mp3"},{"t":"이거 보세요.","en":"Look what I've got.","r":"igeo boseyo.","a":"n_299f1aec13b1.mp3"},{"t":"네, 여기 아파요.","en":"Yes, it hurts here.","r":"ne, yeogi apayo.","a":"n_f4d153eead59.mp3"},{"t":"피곤하지만 행복해요.","en":"I'm tired but happy.","r":"pigonhajiman haengbokaeyo.","a":"n_dd209198d4e6.mp3"},{"t":"배고파요, 뭐 좀 먹어야 해요.","en":"I'm hungry, I need to eat.","r":"baegopayo, mwo jom meogeoya haeyo.","a":"n_c36d95a2fba6.mp3"},{"t":"일어나서 밥 먹어요.","en":"I get up and eat.","r":"ireonaseo bap meogeoyo.","a":"n_b00c4c3db44a.mp3"},{"t":"주문할게요.","en":"I'd like to order, please.","r":"jumunhalgeyo.","a":"n_63b8645a4247.mp3"},{"t":"당신 말이 맞아요.","en":"I know you're right.","r":"dangsin mari majayo.","a":"n_e6e21fcffaca.mp3"},{"t":"당신 말이 맞는 것 같아요.","en":"I think you're right.","r":"dangsin mari manneun geot gatayo.","a":"n_1eff3146a2d8.mp3"},{"t":"자, 이쪽은 카를로스예요.","en":"Look, this is Carlos.","r":"ja, ijjogeun kareulloseuyeyo.","a":"n_f0238aa94e33.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 공부해야 해요.","en":"I have to study today.","r":"oneul gongbuhaeya haeyo.","a":"n_0092667505d3.mp3"},{"t":"아니요, 괜찮아요.","en":"No, that's fine.","r":"aniyo, gwaenchanayo.","a":"n_c50386a08c3b.mp3"},{"t":"아무것도 필요 없어요, 고마워요.","en":"I don't need anything, thanks.","r":"amugeotdo piryo eopseoyo, gomawoyo.","a":"n_d13876e92fbb.mp3"},{"t":"고마워요, 많이 멀어요?","en":"Thanks, is it very far?","r":"gomawoyo, mani meoreoyo?","a":"n_a34f2f5e38d1.mp3"},{"t":"저 할 수 있는 거 알아요.","en":"I know I can do it.","r":"jeo hal su inneun geo arayo.","a":"n_ee48d21f8342.mp3"},{"t":"할 수 있어요, 제가 알아요.","en":"You can do it, I know it.","r":"hal su isseoyo, jega arayo.","a":"n_0fc1b2788b0e.mp3"},{"t":"그냥 혼자 할게요, 고마워요.","en":"I'd rather do it alone, thanks.","r":"geunyang honja halgeyo, gomawoyo.","a":"n_8cd6ca72caba.mp3"},{"t":"일하고 나서 먹어요.","en":"I work and then eat.","r":"ilhago naseo meogeoyo.","a":"n_23584f118ec4.mp3"},{"t":"네, 그 사람 이름은 아나예요.","en":"Yes, her name is Ana.","r":"ne, geu saram ireumeun anayeyo.","a":"n_b304dba0bae9.mp3"},{"t":"이제 가야 해요.","en":"We have to leave now.","r":"ije gaya haeyo.","a":"n_eb0e4b2c9318.mp3"},{"t":"우리 다 가야 해요?","en":"Do we all have to go?","r":"uri da gaya haeyo?","a":"n_519142644790.mp3"},{"t":"맞아요, 좀 쉬어야겠어요.","en":"You're right, I need to rest.","r":"majayo, jom swieoyagesseoyo.","a":"n_7eb609fa274a.mp3"},{"t":"이거 꼭 봐야 해요.","en":"You have to see this.","r":"igeo kkok bwaya haeyo.","a":"n_c22937ef4157.mp3"},{"t":"계산서 주세요.","en":"The check, please.","r":"gyesanseo juseyo.","a":"n_f2f76bc79226.mp3"},{"t":"아니요, 저는 멕시코 출신이에요.","en":"No, I'm from Mexico.","r":"aniyo, jeoneun meksiko chulsini-eyo.","a":"n_d244c8baec46.mp3"},{"t":"네, 제 친구예요.","en":"Yes, she's my friend.","r":"ne, je chinguyeyo.","a":"n_149a6887f5d4.mp3"},{"t":"네, 진짜 배고파요.","en":"Yeah, I'm really hungry.","r":"ne, jinjja baegopayo.","a":"n_4cc1b3819e72.mp3"},{"t":"당신보다 더 많이 먹었어요.","en":"I ate more than you.","r":"dangsinboda deo mani meogeosseoyo.","a":"n_511b10f15422.mp3"},{"t":"안녕하세요, 제 이름은 카를로스예요.","en":"Hi, my name is Carlos.","r":"annyeonghaseyo, je ireumeun kareulloseuyeyo.","a":"n_551de672efa3.mp3"},{"t":"인내심을 가져야 해요.","en":"You need to have patience.","r":"innaesimeul gajyeoya haeyo.","a":"n_96e00348e532.mp3"},{"t":"저 가는 중이라고 전해 줘요.","en":"Tell him I'm on my way.","r":"jeo ganeun jungirago jeonhae jwoyo.","a":"n_00f1e1d36d8c.mp3"},{"t":"미안하다고 전해 줘요.","en":"Tell him I'm sorry.","r":"mianhadago jeonhae jwoyo.","a":"n_f5d447d59512.mp3"},{"t":"반가워요, 저는 카를로스예요.","en":"Nice to meet you, I'm Carlos.","r":"bangawoyo, jeoneun kareulloseuyeyo.","a":"n_0fd198b74989.mp3"},{"t":"반가워요, 제 이름은 아나예요.","en":"Nice to meet you, my name is Ana.","r":"bangawoyo, je ireumeun anayeyo.","a":"n_9879d8568372.mp3"},{"t":"뭐 좀 말할 게 있어요.","en":"I have to tell you something.","r":"mwo jom malhal ge isseoyo.","a":"n_2066dc6a7f98.mp3"},{"t":"여기 봐요, 거기 말고.","en":"Look here, not there.","r":"yeogi bwayo, geogi malgo.","a":"n_15e0aead4e93.mp3"},{"t":"너무 많이 냈어요, 알아요.","en":"I paid too much, I know.","r":"neomu mani naesseoyo, arayo.","a":"n_2d65045f0075.mp3"},{"t":"열이 나는 것 같아요.","en":"I think I have a fever.","r":"yeori naneun geot gatayo.","a":"n_24713018ec79.mp3"}]}